==Private life==
In April 2024, it was announced by [[Antenna (record label)|Antenna Entertainment]] that Song is in a romantic relationship with one of their artists, singer [[Mijoo|Lee Mijoo]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=이미주♥송범근, 3살 연상연하 커플 탄생‥"호감 갖고 만나는 중" |trans-title=Lee Mi-joo ♥ Song Bum-Keun, a couple 3 years younger than 3 years older... "Meeting with interest" |url=https://m.entertain.naver.com/now/article/112/0003692506 |access-date=2024-04-18 |website=m.entertain.naver.com}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-04-18 |title=[단독] 이미주, 축구선수 송범근과 열애 중…가수♥스포츠 스타 커플 탄생 |trans-title=[Exclusive] Lee Mi-joo is in a relationship with soccer player Song Bum-Keun... Singer♥Sports star couple born |url=http://enter.etoday.co.kr/news/view/257851 |access-date=2024-04-18 |website=비즈엔터 |language=ko}}</ref> In February 2025, It was reported that the two had broken up.<ref>{{Cite web |last=기자 |first=박서연 |title=&quot;나 괜찮다&quot; 이미주, 송범근과 결별 인정&hellip;주우재 &quot;옆에 있다 없으면 허전&quot; 위로 [놀뭐](종합) |trans-title="I'm okay," Lee Mi-joo admits to breaking up with Song Beom-geun... Joo Woo-jae comforts her, saying, "I feel empty without you." [Nolmoo] (Comprehensive) |url=https://mydaily.co.kr/page/view/2025020119080774218 |access-date=2025-11-25 |website=마이데일리 |language=ko}}</ref>

